%header.pcheader
  .header-inner
    .header-title
      .header-logo
        =link_to "/", class: "frema-icon" do
          = image_tag src="logo.png", class: "FURIMA-btn"
      .header-searchbox
        %form.search-box
          %input{type: "text", class: "search-box-input", id: "seach-input", name: "key", placeholder: "キーワードから探す"}
          %button{type: "submit", class: "search-submitbtn"} 
            .header-icon
              = image_tag src="icon-search 1.png", class: "Search-btn"
    .header-nav
      %ul.left-list
        %li.list-category
          = link_to "#" do
            = "カテゴリー"
        %li.list-bland
          = link_to "#" do
            = "ブランド"
      %ul.right-list
        %li.list-login
          = link_to "#" do
            = "ログイン"
        %li.list-signup
          = link_to "#" do
            = "新規登録"
.main
  %section.fv
    .content
      %h2.content-title 人生を変えるフリマアプリ
      %p.content-text
        FURIMAはだれでもかんたんに出品・購入できる
        %br
        フリマアプリです。
      .content-btn
        =link_to "/" do
          = image_tag src="Download_on_the_App_Store_Badge_US-UK_blk_092917.png", class: "apple"
        =link_to "/" do
          = image_tag src="1google-play-badge.png", class: "google"
  %section.reason
    %h2.sub-title FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
    %ul.reason-lists
      %li.reason-list
        .list-pic
          %span.number 1
          = image_tag src="pict-reason-01.jpg"
        %h3.list-text 3分ですぐに出品
        %p.list-comment スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
      %li.reason-list
        .list-pic
          %span.number 2
          = image_tag src="pict-reason-02.jpg"
        %h3.list-text シンプルで使いやすい
        %p.list-comment めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
      %li.reason-list
        .list-pic
          %span.number 3
          = image_tag src="pict-reason-03.jpg"
        %h3.list-text 手数料業界最安
        %p.list-comment 最大3%でお得に出品&購入!
  %section.sv
